To use mind ide, you must add an directory entry with this value ${workspace_loc:build} in your target platform 
(go to preference pages in 'Plug-ins Development/Target Platform', 
	select the active platform and click on add button, 
	select 'directory' and enter this value '${workspace_loc:build}')
or put 
	- org.ow2.mind.fractal-adl-bundle_0.2-alpha-2-SNAPSHOT.jar and 
	- org.ow2.mind.fractal-adl-bundle.source_0.2-alpha-2-SNAPSHOT.jar
in the eclipse/dropins folder 